This project contains source code for the Akraino Regional Controller Feature Project.
This is the second implementation of a regional controller (the first was for Network Cloud only).
The Wiki for this FP is at https://wiki.akraino.org/display/AK/Akraino+Regional+Controller

Contents of the subdirectories are:
docker        - Dockerfiles and other source to create the two Docker containers
scripts       - Scripts to start/stop the regional controller, and to load data into the RC.
src           - Java code for the Regional Controller API server
src/site/docs - Documentation in RST format
